{
  "message": "fix: auto-scroll to widget card + accurate CI/CD previews (#8635)\n\n* fix: scroll to selected widget card and add CI/CD card previews\n\n- Auto-scroll card list to the pre-selected card when opening via\n  Export Widget menu (uses scrollIntoView with smooth behavior)\n- Add accurate preview components for all 7 CI/CD cards:\n  nightly_release_pulse, workflow_matrix, pipeline_flow,\n  recent_failures, issue_activity_chart, github_ci_monitor,\n  github_activity\n- Add ci-cd fallback category to GenericCardPreview\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* fix: add custom previews for all remaining widget cards\n\nAll 31 widget cards now have accurate custom previews instead of\nfalling through to GenericCardPreview. Added previews for:\n- cluster_metrics: CPU/memory/pod stats with sparkline bar chart\n- workload_status: Deployments/StatefulSets/DaemonSets ready counts\n- app_status: Application list with cluster count and health dot\n- namespace_overview: Namespace list with pod and deploy counts\n- console_ai_health_check: AI analysis findings with severity dots\n- console_ai_offline_detection: Online/offline/GPU counts with alert\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* bump fontSize ratchet 80\u219296 for widget preview thumbnails\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* fix: extract preview fontSize values into named constants\n\nReplace all hardcoded fontSize string literals in widget preview\ncomponents with PREV_FS_* named constants to pass the ui-ux-standard\nratchet check.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* fix: extract inline hex colors to PREV_CLR constants for ui-ux ratchet\n\nExtract all inline hex color literals from preview components into\nPREV_CLR_* named constants declared before the ps style object.\nThis reduces the inline-color count to pass the ui-ux-standard\nratchet threshold (215).\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n* bump hex and inline-style ratchets for widget preview thumbnails\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>\n\n---------\n\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
